host-llvm-system
================

This is a Buildroot host-only package that symlinks the Debian build
container's preinstalled LLVM/Clang/libclc toolchain (LLVM 22 from
apt.llvm.org) into $(HOST_DIR) so that Buildroot consumers can use it
instead of building host-llvm, host-clang and host-libclc from source.

Container packages required:
  llvm-22 llvm-22-dev clang-22 clang-tools-22 libllvm22
  libclang1-22 libclang-cpp22 libclang-common-22-dev
  libclang-22-dev libclc-22-dev

It provides the virtual Buildroot packages:
  host-llvm host-clang host-libclc

License: Apache-2.0 with LLVM-exception (matching the LLVM project).
